{"task": "crystallographic-wyckoff-position-analysis", "condition": "no_skill", "repeat": 1, "skill_id": null, "retrieval_correct": null, "judged_pass": false, "judged_score": 1, "judge_reason": "Agent's solution does not match the required function signature 'analyze_wyckoff_positions' and lacks structured output format per verifier expectations.", "solver_tokens": 2653, "judge_tokens": 931, "solution_text": "```python\n#!/usr/bin/env python3\nimport os\nfrom pymatgen.core import Structure\nfrom pymatgen.symmetry.analyzer import SpaceGroupAnalyzer\n\ndef process_cif(file_path):\n    try:\n        struct = Structure.from_file(file_path)\n        sga = SpaceGroupAnalyzer(struct)\n        space_group = sga.get_space_group_symbol()\n        wyckoff = sga.get_wyckoff_positions()\n        \n        print(f\"File: {file_path}\")\n        print(f\"Space Group: {space_group}\")\n        print(\"Wyckoff Positions:\")\n        for wp in wyckoff:\n            print(f\"  {wp.label} (multiplicity: {wp.multiplicity}): {wp.site_symmetry}\")\n        print(\"\\n\")\n        return True\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"Error processing {file_path}: {e}\")\n        return False\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    cif_files = [f for f in os.listdir() if f.endswith('.cif')]\n    if not cif_files:\n        print(\"No CIF files found.\")\n        exit(1)\n    for cif in cif_files:\n        process_cif(cif)\n```"}
