{"task": "dialogue-parser", "condition": "retrieved_top1_full", "repeat": 1, "skill_id": "jeremylongshore--graphviz-dot-generator", "retrieval_correct": false, "judged_pass": false, "judged_score": 1, "judge_reason": "Agent's solution does not match oracle's structured JSON format with node types and proper IDs, and fails to handle choices and branching logic.", "solver_tokens": 4917, "judge_tokens": 1025, "solution_text": "```python\nimport json\nimport sys\n\ndef parse_dialogue(filename):\n    nodes = []\n    edges = []\n    with open(filename, 'r') as f:\n        lines = f.readlines()\n    for i, line in enumerate(lines):\n        line = line.strip()\n        if not line:\n            continue\n        if ':' in line:\n            speaker, text = line.split(':', 1)\n            speaker = speaker.strip()\n            text = text.strip()\n        else:\n            speaker = \"Unknown\"\n            text = line\n        nodes.append({\n            \"id\": i,\n            \"speaker\": speaker,\n            \"text\": text\n        })\n        if i > 0:\n            edges.append({\n                \"from\": i-1,\n                \"to\": i\n            })\n    return {\"nodes\": nodes, \"edges\": edges}\n\ndef generate_dot(graph):\n    dot = \"digraph {\\n\"\n    for node in graph[\"nodes\"]:\n        label = f\"{node['speaker']}: {node['text']}\"\n        dot += f'  {node[\"id\"]} [label=\"{label}\"];\\n'\n    for edge in graph[\"edges\"]:\n        dot += f'  {edge[\"from\"]} -> {edge[\"to\"]};\\n'\n    dot += \"}\"\n    return dot\n\ndef main():\n    input_file = \"/app/script.txt\"\n    output_json = \"/app/dialogue.json\"\n    output_dot = \"/app/dialogue.dot\"\n    \n    graph = parse_dialogue(input_file)\n    with open(output_json, 'w') as f:\n        json.dump(graph, f, indent=2)\n    \n    dot_content = generate_dot(graph)\n    with open(output_dot, 'w') as f:\n        f.write(dot_content)\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()\n```"}
